WEBVTT

00:03:58.327 --> 00:04:00.696
with fireworks and a crowd of thousands.

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:03.696
LeBron predicted they would
be winning championships for years.

00:04:03.720 --> 00:04:05.936
LeBron James:
It's going to be easy. I mean --

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:09.096
Announcer: But we also know
you three kings came down here

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:10.456
to win championships.

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:11.936
LeBron, tell us about that.

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:14.856
LJ: Not two, not three, not four,

00:04:14.880 --> 00:04:18.600
not five, not six, not seven.

00:04:19.240 --> 00:04:21.416
AG: But they struggled
to even win close games

00:04:21.440 --> 00:04:23.016
in the regular seasons.

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:26.736
They had three players who were all
used to taking the game-winning shot.

00:04:26.760 --> 00:04:29.016
ML: There are other things
basketball players do

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:30.296
that are very valuable